task.summary: 1.Create test dir, using junit 4 2.Add MyList.java(some list problems)

1. Compare the effect between String plus(+)、StringBuilder.append、StringBuffer.append. result: 10000 chars & 10 loops String Plus Average : 566ms String Builder Average : 0ms String Buffer Average : 0ms
result: 1000000 chars & 10 loops without testing String Plus String Builder Average : 29ms String Buffer Average : 59ms
Conclusion : String plus(+) is very slow while StringBuilder is bit of faster than StringBuffer
2. Translate between int and char in ascii code Problems: * Can't print ascii code 13 * Not all Chinese can be represent by ascii code, Try unicode 3. Try some new features in java 8 (eg: lambda, method interface...)
